### Debug del Descubrimiento MCP

@baseUrl = http://localhost:5085
@apiKey = dev-key-1

### 1. Verificar que el servidor esté funcionando
GET {{baseUrl}}/health/live

### 2. Crear un servidor MCP simple
# @name createServer
POST {{baseUrl}}/mcp/servers
Content-Type: application/json
x-api-key: {{apiKey}}

{
  "name": "Debug MCP Server",
  "baseUrl": "http://localhost:8970",
  "authType": "none"
}

### 3. Verificar que se creó el servidor
GET {{baseUrl}}/mcp/servers
x-api-key: {{apiKey}}

### 4. Intentar descubrimiento HTTP directo al servidor MCP
POST http://localhost:8970
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "jsonrpc": "2.0",
  "id": "test-1",
  "method": "tools/list",
  "params": {}
}

### 5. Intentar descubrimiento a través de nuestra API
# @name discoverTools
POST {{baseUrl}}/mcp/servers/{{createServer.response.body.id}}/discover
x-api-key: {{apiKey}}

### 6. Verificar respuesta del descubrimiento
GET {{baseUrl}}/mcp/tools?serverId={{createServer.response.body.id}}
x-api-key: {{apiKey}}

### 7. Verificar todas las herramientas
GET {{baseUrl}}/mcp/tools/all
x-api-key: {{apiKey}}

